snippet.title: Blade & Wings: Fantasy 3D Anime MMORPG Game
snippet.description: For too long, players have become accustomed to battling against just NPCs in traditional games. Blade & Wings uniquely changes this and reverses the identity between NPC and player. In Blade & Wings, you become the NPC and those who surround you are the players and enemies. Join us and show your enemies no mercy as you throw them out of this world.
